<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SPORTMATCH — 페이지 없음</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;0,9..40,700;1,9..40,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Bebas+Neue&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>
<div class="error-page">
  <div class="error-bg-number">404</div>

  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center">
    <div class="error-emoji">🔍</div>
    <div class="error-code">404 · Not Found</div>
    <div class="error-title">페이지를 찾을 수 없어요</div>
    <div class="url-display"><%= typeof requestUrl !== 'undefined' ? requestUrl : '요청하신 주소' %></div>
    <div class="error-desc">
      주소가 잘못되었거나 삭제된 페이지예요.<br>
      아래 링크에서 원하는 항목을 찾아보세요!
    </div>
    <div class="error-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-accent btn-lg" onclick="location.href='/'">🏠 홈으로 돌아가기</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="history.back()">← 이전으로</button>
    </div>

    <div class="suggest-section">
      <div class="suggest-title">이런 페이지는 어때요?</div>
      <div class="suggest-grid">
        <a class="suggest-card" href="/map">
          <div class="suggest-card-emoji">🗺️</div>
          <div><div class="suggest-card-text">매칭 지도</div><div class="suggest-card-sub">내 주변 매칭 찾기</div></div>
        </a>
        <a class="suggest-card" href="/regular">
          <div class="suggest-card-emoji">🔁</div>
          <div><div class="suggest-card-text">정기 모임</div><div class="suggest-card-sub">클럽 & 정기모임 참가</div></div>
        </a>
        <a class="suggest-card" href="/trade">
          <div class="suggest-card-emoji">🛒</div>
          <div><div class="suggest-card-text">장비 거래</div><div class="suggest-card-sub">스포츠 용품 사고팔기</div></div>
        </a>
        <a class="suggest-card" href="/community">
          <div class="suggest-card-emoji">💬</div>
          <div><div class="suggest-card-text">커뮤니티</div><div class="suggest-card-sub">자유게시판 & 꿀팁</div></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
